      <title>安装ArchLinux的简单记录</title>
      <link href="/2018/08/05/archlinux-installion-guide/"/>
      <url>/2018/08/05/archlinux-installion-guide/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h3 id="Warning"><a href="#Warning" class="headerlink" title="Warning"></a>Warning</h3><p>对分区表的任何操作都有可能损坏数据，请谨慎操作。</p><hr><h3 id="Pre-Installion"><a href="#Pre-Installion" class="headerlink" title="Pre-Installion"></a>Pre-Installion</h3><p>先进入ArchISO(这个太简单了，不罗嗦啦)。</p><p>验证是否接入有限网。<br>-<br><code># ping archlinux.org</code></p><p>更新软件时钟。<br>-<br><code># timedatectl set-ntp true</code></p><p>对磁盘进行分区。<br>-<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># fdisk -l</span><br><span class="line"># fdisk /dev/sda </span><br><span class="line">fdisk&gt; d-n-p-1</span><br><span class="line">fdisk&gt; w</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>格式化新建分区。<br>-<br><code># mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda1</code></p><p>在其他分区开启SWAP。<br>-<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># mkswap /dev/sda2</span><br><span class="line"># swapon /dev/sda2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><h3 id="Installion"><a href="#Installion" class="headerlink" title="Installion"></a>Installion</h3><p>将准备安装ArchLinux的分区挂载到/mnt。<br>-<br><code># mount /dev/sda1 /mnt</code></p><p>安装base base-devel软件包组。<br>-<br><code># pacstrap /mnt base base-devel vim</code></p><hr><h3 id="Configure"><a href="#Configure" class="headerlink" title="Configure"></a>Configure</h3><p>将FSTAB文件注入/etc。<br>-<br><code># genfstab - U /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab</code></p><p>进入已安装的ArchLinux。<br>-<br><code># arch-chroot /mnt</code></p><p>设置时区。<br>-<br><code># ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime</code></p><p>修改主机名。<br>-<br><code># hostnamectl set-hostname NAME</code></p><p>更改ROOT用户密码。<br>-<br><code># passwd</code></p><hr><h3 id="After-Installion"><a href="#After-Installion" class="headerlink" title="After Installion"></a>After Installion</h3><p>安装GRUB。<br>-<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># pacman -Sy</span><br><span class="line"># pacman -S grub</span><br><span class="line"># mkdir -p ~/mnt &amp;&amp; mount &#123;WINDOWS&#125; ~/mnt</span><br><span class="line"># grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>退出CHROOT环境。<br>-<br><code># exit</code></p><p>解除挂载并重启。<br>-<br><code># umount -R /mnt &amp;&amp; reboot</code></p><p>配置非ROOT用户。<br>-<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># useradd -g users -G wheel -s /bin/bash -m NAME</span><br><span class="line"># passwd NAME</span><br><span class="line"># vim /etc/sudoers </span><br><span class="line">vim&gt; NAME ALL_(ALL)</span><br><span class="line"># su NAME</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>安装中文支持。<br>-<br><code>$ sudo pacamn -S wqy-microhei fcitx fcitx-im fcitx-googlepinyin</code></p><p>安装图形界面，显卡驱动，声卡驱动，窗口管理器。<br>-<br><code>$ sudo pacman -S xorg xorg-xinit alsa-utils xf86-video-{nouveau|intel} herbstluftwm</code></p><p>BASHRC &amp; XINITRC。<br>-<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.bashrc&gt;</span><br><span class="line">export PS1=&apos;\[\e[31;40m\]\u\e[0m@\h \W \$\n-&gt;&apos;</span><br><span class="line">.xinitrc&gt;</span><br><span class="line">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export XMODIFIERS=&quot;@im=fcitx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">export LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8</span><br><span class="line">exec herbstluftwm</span><br><span class="line">exec fcitx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>进入图形界面。<br>-<br><code>startx</code></p><p>欢迎来到LINUX的世界。</p><p><img src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/75d7e97fgy1ft0o2y7g7rj20b92bf7sf.jpg" alt="avatar"></p><hr><h3 id="Cnachen-Related-Linki"><a href="#Cnachen-Related-Linki" class="headerlink" title="Cnachen Related Linki"></a>Cnachen Related Linki</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/Cnachen?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></p><p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/mxdfpha" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit</a></p><p><a href="https://music.163.com/#/user/home?id=265406348" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NetEase Cloud Music</a></p><p><a href="https://space.bilibili.com/9848797/#/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BiliBili</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
